Detailed Description

cvmx_dpi_srio_rx_bell_seq#

This register contains the value of the sequence counter when the doorbell was received and a shadow copy of the Bell FIFO Count that can be read without emptying the FIFO. This register must be read prior to corresponding DPI_SRIO_RX_BELL register to link the doorbell and sequence number.

Information on the Doorbell Allocation can be found in SRIO()_RX_BELL_CTRL.
